    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really nice shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a solid car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of love here and there from regular use, but it runs like a dream and the interior is super comfy and clean. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have! Drop me a message if you want to come see it or take it for a spin!",
