    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a formidable example of BMW M's high-revving peak, powered by the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 delivering 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, the mechanical feedback is unparalleled. This chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains structurally rigid, providing exceptional lateral grip and turn-in precision. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and induction systems perform optimally. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains tight and the exhaust note is visceral. It is a mechanically sound, driver-focused machine ready for the canyon or the circuit.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
