    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior features a deep Midnight Blue finish that still holds a brilliant shine, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the premium charcoal leather interior remains supple; while there is light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the cabin is free of tears, odors, or stains. All technological features, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and the upgraded infotainment system, are in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is sound, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection. We have just performed a fresh oil change and replaced the cabin air filter. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. Complete service records are available to verify its history of on-time maintenance. This is a solid, honest vehicle ready for its next journey.",
